g the Normans. In the later Middle Ages it was overtaken by   John  , but continued to run second to that name until the 20th century, when the picture became more fragmented."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"William Caynton was born about 1290, in Edgmond, Shropshire, England, United Kingdom. He married Mrs Caynton about 1320, in Shropshire, England, United Kingdom."},"et":{"Abt 1290–":"umbes 1290–Surnud","1299–Female":"1299–Surnud","1320–Male":"1320–Surnud","1290–Male":"1290–Surnud","Abt 1320":"umbes 1320","1299":"1299","1320":"1320","Abt 1290":"umbes 1290","1290":"1290","Caynton Manor, Edgmond, Shropshire, England, United Kingdom":"Edgmond, Shropshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Salop, England":"Shropshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"Abt 1290–":"noin 1290–Kuollut","1299–Female":"1299–Kuollut","1320–Male":"1320–Kuollut","1290–Male":"1290–Kuollut","Abt 1320":"noin 1320","1299":"1299","1320":"1320","Abt 1290":"noin 1290","1290":"1290","Caynton Manor, Edgmond, Shropshire, England, United Kingdom":"Edgmond, Shropshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Salop, England":"Shropshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"Abt 1290–":"environ 1290–Décédé","1299–Female":"1299–Décédée","1320–Male":"1320–Décédé","1290–Male":"1290–Décédé","Abt 1320":"environ 1320","1299":"1299","1320":"1320","Abt 1290":"environ 1290","1290":"1290","Caynton Manor, Edgmond, Shropshire, England, United Kingdom":"Edgmond, Shropshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","Salop, England":"Shropshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"William Caynton est né environ 1290, à Edgmond, Shropshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Il a épousé Mrs Caynton environ 1320, à Shropshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni."},"de":{"Abt 1290–":"um 1290–Verstorben","1299–Female":"1299–Verstorben","1320–Male":"1320–Verstorben","1290–Male":"1290–Verstorben","Abt 1320":"um 1320","1299":"1299","1320":"1320","Abt 1290":"um 1290","1290":"1290","Caynton Manor, Edgmond, Shropshire, England, United Kingdom":"Edgmond, Shropshire